			<h2><strong>Shingle Roof Systems</strong></h2>

			<p class="lead">A shingle roof installed by Bryce Roofing's expert installers is a roof that will provide protection from the elements for decades and comes with a ten year <em>No Worries</em> workmanship warranty for your peace of mind</p>

			<p>Shingle roofs are a cost-effective solution for your home or business. Shingle roofs come in a wide variety of styles and warranties including many designer styles to enhance your homes curb appeal.  Bryce Roofing can install a high performance, high value shingle roof system that's right for you.</p>
		</div>
